Task Management Service
=======================

CRUD Operations

operation	http-method
Create		POST
Retrieve	GET
Update	        UPDATE
Delete	        DELETE

Task service API
=================
Resource name : task

Api Endpoint's:

/task  -> GET, POST, DELETE
/task/<id> -> GET,PUT,DELETE



Test the application
====================



POST   http://localhost:8080/taskrestapp/task
       Content-Type: application/json
       Body: { "description": "Test REST", "completed": false }

GET    http://localhost:8080/taskrestapp/task

DELETE http://localhost:8080/taskrestapp/task/1
